  <title>Delete User</title>
  <para>
    A user can be deleted by making a <literal>DELETE</literal> request using the IGS SCIM Provisioning implementation <emphasis role="strong">/Users</emphasis> endpoint with an existing user ID.
  </para>
  <section xml:id="api-usr-delete-not">
    <title>Not supported</title>
    <para>
      The IGS SCIM Provisioning implementation does not support the following aspects of this API operation.
    </para>
    <itemizedlist mark='bullet'>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          None
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </section>
  <section xml:id="api-usr-delete-con">
    <title>Constraints</title>
    <para>
